cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.IT. 

This paper focuses on developing a decentralized resource allocation mechanism for V2V communications based on deep reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also uses deep reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves decision-making by autonomous agents, which is related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper deals with optimizing the use of limited resources, which is related to cs.IT (Information Theory).
